OL,6,FA mother who killed her 6-year-old son
OL,7,Fin Swansea with a handsaw has been
OL,8,Fsentenced to a indefinite hospital
OL,9,Forder under section 37 of the Mental
OL,10,FHealth Act of 1983.
OL,12,FKarolina Zurawska, 42, pleaded guilty
OL,13,Fto the manslaughter of Alexander
OL,14,FZurawski on the grounds of diminished
OL,15,Fresponsibility, when she killed him at
OL,16,Ftheir home on Cwm Du Close in August
OL,17,Flast year.
OL,19,FMs Zurawska was also sentenced for the
OL,20,Fattempted murder of her father,
OL,21,FKrzysztof Siwy
