OL,6,FToday, a court heard how Ms Zurawska
OL,7,Fattempted to stab her father on three
OL,8,Fseparate occasions on the day she
OL,9,Fkilled Alexander.
OL,11,FWhen Mr Siwy visited his daughter on
OL,12,Fthe morning of Alexander's death, he
OL,13,Fdescribed his daughter as mumbling and
OL,14,Fabsent.
OL,16,FIn a witness statement read to the
OL,17,Fcourt, Mr Siwy described how his
OL,18,Fdaughter reached for a knife and told
OL,19,Fhim, 'Dad, I must kill you' before
OL,20,Fslashing him in the neck.
