OL,6,FKrzysztof Siwy managed to restrain his
OL,7,Fdaughter but could not remove
OL,8,FAlexander from the family home.
OL,10,FDespite calling family members in
OL,11,FPoland to raise concerns about Ms
OL,12,FZurawska's behaviour, Mr Siwy failed
OL,13,Fto call the police.
OL,15,FAt 8:30 pm on the 28th of August 2024,
OL,16,Fneighbours found Ms Zurawska kneeling
OL,17,Fbeside Alexander with a handsaw at her
OL,18,Fside.
