OL,6,FWitnesses described seeing Alexander
OL,7,Flying in the hallway of his home,
OL,8,Fafter screams were heard coming from
OL,9,Fthe family home.
OL,11,FParamedics worked to save Alexander,
OL,12,Fbut he was declared dead at the scene.
OL,14,FSwansea Crown Court heard, Ms Zurawska
OL,15,Fwas described as suffering from
OL,16,FParanoid Schizophrenia, which
OL,17,Fsubstantially impacted her ability to
OL,18,Funderstand what she was doing.
