OL,6,FIn an impact statement read to the
OL,7,Fcourt, Krzysztof Siwy said, "Why did
OL,8,Fthis happen? I was able to defend
OL,9,Fmyself, but I was unable to defend
OL,10,FAlexander."
OL,12,F"I was unable to think logically and
OL,13,Frationally. If I had called the
OL,14,Fpolice, this tragedy would not have
OL,15,Fhappened. I will have to carry this
OL,16,Fburden for the rest of my life. My
OL,17,Flife is no longer as it used to be."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/10
