OL,6,F"I love my daughter, and I do not
OL,7,Fblame her for what happened. I need to
OL,8,Fbe able to support Karolina, but I
OL,9,Fdon't know what the future holds for
OL,10,Fme."
OL,12,FJudge Paul Thomas QC said, "The often
OL,13,Foverused word of tragic does not begin
OL,14,Fto reflect the awfulness that happened
OL,15,Fthat day to Alexander. Those who know
OL,16,Fyou and your relationship with
OL,17,FAlexander have described you as a
OL,18,Fdoting, loving, caring mother."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/10
