OL,3,CMother given hospital order after
OL,4,Ckilling six-year-old son with handsaw
OL,6,F"You are not a wicked mother, far from
OL,7,Fit - you are a mother whose mental
OL,8,Fstate deteriorated over your care of
OL,9,FAlexander. You did something to
OL,10,FAlexander that would never have
OL,11,Fentered your mind had it not been for
OL,12,Fyour mental state."
OL,14,F"I entirely agree with the three
OL,15,Fpsychiatrists that this is a case that
OL,16,Fcalls not for punishment but for
OL,17,Fongoing lifelong medical help. Even if
OL,18,Fyou do recover mentally, the burden of
OL,19,Fwhat happened will always be with you."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/10
