OL,6,FIn a statement released after his
OL,7,Fdeath Alexander's family described him
OL,8,Fas a "very kind child".
OL,10,FThey said: "Alexander was always well-
OL,11,Fbehaved and never naughty. He was very
OL,12,Fclever and very mature for his age. He
OL,13,Fhad a great understanding of facts.
OL,15,F"Alexander was always helpful, always
OL,16,Feager to assist with cooking and
OL,17,Fcleaning. Alexander spoke both English
OL,18,Fand Polish and would often correct his
OL,19,Fparents with their English if they got
OL,20,Fwords wrong. He was amazing."
