OL,8,Fsaid: "Alexander was an extremely
OL,9,Floved and popular boy amongst his
OL,10,Fpeers, staff and with all who knew him.
OL,12,F"He is sadly missed by us all. As a
OL,13,Fschool we are working to create a
OL,14,Fsensory garden in his memory, that
OL,15,Fwill provide a calming and reflective
OL,16,Farea that further promotes the well-
OL,17,Fbeing of our learners."
